data.description: NEW Price! So don’t miss this well-kept (2nd owner) 4 bed 1.5 bath ranch home in a desirable Allouez location!!  Boasting 1,829 sqft of living space, this home has plenty to offer! You will enjoy the bright & open kitchen, large bedrooms featuring hardwood flooring, ample storage throughout, and a spacious finished lower level level with egressed 4th bedroom, a huge family room, 1/2 bath, and a bonus 21' x 4' shelved storage area/closet. The fenced-in backyard is a fantastic outdoor space for all of your entertaining needs w/deck/patio access right off the kitchen! The one car garage is extra deep allowing for workbench, etc. Seller updates include new furnace 2019. Room to add finishing touches to make this charming home your own.
